# Screen layout

Use `ScreenLayout` for auth, onboarding, and flow screens. Never ad-hoc `pt-24` or custom sticky footers.

## Structure

| Zone | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Header | `PageFixedHeader` via `ScreenLayout` | Always reserve slot (`reserveHeader`) on intro steps |
| Body | scrollable `flex-1` | Offset from `screenHeaderBodyOffset(variant)` |
| Footer | `ScreenFooter` / `HaguFlowCta` | Pinned bottom, `h-16` buttons, same safe-area |

## Header variants

- `brand` / `flowHagu` / `none` → same body offset (45px glass chrome)
- `flowHagee` → taller offset (back + progress)

## Tokens

Defined in [`screen-layout.tsx`](components/ui/screen-layout.tsx) and [`page-shell.tsx`](components/ui/page-shell.tsx):

- `PAGE_HEADER_TOP_PADDING`
- `PAGE_FIXED_HEADER_OFFSET`
- `PAGE_HAGEE_FLOW_HEADER_OFFSET`

## View transition

Entry hero and glass header share `hagu-brand-transition` (`view-transition-name: hagu-brand`).
